{{version030}}
{{flavour|Creates a cloud of spectral mist, dealing minor damage to all creatures other than the undead. Dangerous but short-lived spectral undead creatures will coalesce from the mist over time.}}

'''Spectral Cloud''' is a monster-only spell which creates [[cloud]]s of ghostly flame. These deal a small amount of partially-irresistible [[negative energy]] damage to anything caught inside them, though the undead are immune to this. They also occasionally spawn short-lived [[spectral thing]]s which immediately attack you. Followers of [[Yredelemnul]] are completely immune to these clouds.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*Prior to [[0.19]], this spell could heal undead.
*Prior to [[0.17]], Spectral Cloud was called Ghostly Flames.
*Ghostly Flames was added in [[0.13]].

[[Category:Monster spells]]
